OL,6,FThey could face legal action if they
OL,7,Ffail to comply.
OL,9,FPC Molisa McGinnis, of Lincolnshire
OL,10,FPolice, said: "There may be some who
OL,11,Fsay that a piece of paper won't solve
OL,12,Fanything, but this is a really
OL,13,Fimportant tool in tackling anti-social
OL,14,Fbehaviour because it gives us an
OL,15,Fevidence base to intervene swiftly
OL,16,Fwith other measures if things don't
OL,17,Fchange."
OL,19,FProblems escalated last summer in
OL,20,Fareas including Central Car Park,
OL,21,FCornhill and High Street.
