OL,4,Ccontracts after city centre trouble
OL,6,FThere were complaints of youths
OL,7,Fthreatening shop customers, refusing
OL,8,Fto leave stores, riding e-scooters and
OL,9,Fbikes on public footways and drinking.
OL,11,FPolice initially issued 190 advice
OL,12,Fletters, followed by a further 41
OL,13,Fwarning letters.
OL,15,FPC McGinnis said: "We knew that we
OL,16,Fneeded to do something, and engaging
OL,17,Fthese young people in a way that would
OL,18,Fhelp them understand what was and
OL,19,Fwasn't okay was the way to go.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
