OL,6,F"We also had additional officers
OL,7,Ftasked with patrols, and the first
OL,8,Fstep in most cases was to issue an
OL,9,Finitial warning to the children
OL,10,Finvolved, which includes speaking to
OL,11,Ftheir parents or legal guardians.
OL,13,F"When the advice and warning letters
OL,14,Fdidn't hit home, and those children
OL,15,Fcontinued to act in such an
OL,16,Funacceptable way, they had to attend
OL,17,Fthe police station and sit down with a
OL,18,FSergeant and someone from the council
OL,19,Fwhile the contract is drawn up."
