OL,6,FThe contracts last for an initial six
OL,7,Fmonths, but can be extended.
OL,9,FBen Jackson, anti-social behaviour and
OL,10,Flicensing manager at City of Lincoln
OL,11,FCouncil, said: "Unfortunately, there
OL,12,Fare some youths who aren't taking
OL,13,Fnotice of these warnings. We want
OL,14,Fthese individuals and their parents to
OL,15,Fbe aware that the council can, and
OL,16,Fwill, consider legal action."
